I was pretty depressed during my second college semester this year. I've also had problems paying attention in class, getting up early in the morning, etc. as early as I can remember.. (which in the past has gotten me fired from numerous jobs.. and also gotten me bad grades in high school.... and also gotten my parents called in to Teacher's meetings back in primary school .. etc) .
&nbsp;
.. Although .. to me I don't feel it's a 'disease' so much as it is the fact that I simply don't function well in the 9-5 corporate world. I'm more of a nocturnal creature .. ... If I could be left alone so I can do my programming, animations, video editing, etc. at my own place, in my own time ... and have the freedom to get up whenever I want, and also have enough income to not have to be a nervous wreck when it comes to paying the bills ... I'd probably be a much, much happier person.
